			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It's a max of 2mbits capable, as in, there are enough address lines (A0-A17) but there were only 2 Japanese games that used a 1mbit sram (A0-A16).   The 1L8B I have seen with 1mbit and 512k srams mounted on them.  Beyond these two 1mbit sram games, there's a few that use 512k, otherwise all the others are 256 and 64k (1L5b and 1L3b respectively).</div>

