					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Anything above 1mbit BW-RAM 32mbit ROM requires the Super MMC decoder which is found on the chip. As far as I'm aware no game used anything requiring this amount, so I'm not sure if emu devs have fully implemented it. :p<br /><br />Thanks for clearing this up guys. It seems there's a few places where the manual isn't perfect.<br /><br />~Molive</div>

